<ansi fg="black-bold">.:</ansi> <ansi fg="magenta">Help for </ansi><ansi fg="command">smarts</ansi>

<ansi fg="cyan">Smarts</ansi> measures your intellect and tactical awareness. A sharper mind finds
weaknesses others miss.

<ansi fg="yellow">Combat</ansi>

* Increases your critical hit chance. The smarter you are compared to your
  opponent, the more often you land a decisive blow (up to {{ config "GamePlay.Combat.CritChanceMax" }}% crit chance).

<ansi fg="yellow">Magic</ansi>

* Improves your spellcasting success, helping you land spells more reliably.

<ansi fg="yellow">Exploration</ansi>

* Expands how many rooms your map can hold, letting you chart larger areas
  before older sections fade from memory.
</ansi>
